  <brief_title>The Efficacy of Vocal Function Exercises for Laryngeal Cancers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Investigating the Efficacy of Vocal Function Exercises in the Treatment of Voice Problems in Adults Treated With Radiation Therapy for Laryngeal Cancers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
